reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Very bright LEDs
reviews.reviewText: I usually only read reviews and rarely leave them but I had to say that these are actually awesome. These lights are SUPER bright! I wish I had taken before and after picures. I went from having to use the flashlight on my phone to see stuff even with all of the interior lights on in my 2021 Ram to being able to see EVERYTHING! I even have a few extra lights left over that I didn't even use so if some go out in the future, I already have replacements.
